Work in progress updates to git-delete-both.sh and git-stash-inspector.sh:

1. git-delete-both.sh improvements:
   - Added TODO: handle missing upstream
   - Added upstream existence check before attempting deletion
   - Cleaner error handling when upstream doesn't exist
   - Renamed variables for clarity (local/remote -> local_ref/remote_ref)
   - Better separation of logic with comments

2. git-stash-inspector.sh improvements:
   - Added proper OPTIONS_SPEC for git rev-parse --parseopt
   - Implemented standard option parsing (--help support)
   - Made branch name optional (defaults to current branch)
   - Uses git rev-parse --abbrev-ref HEAD as fallback
   - More robust argument handling

